snippet.title: Tongue Cancer, Squamous Cell Carcinoma in Young People, Do you have it Survive It!_(new)
snippet.description:
Tongue Cancer, Squamous Cell Carcinoma in Young People, Do you have it Survive It!_(new)
Toegevoegd door Dentalmainframe.com een week geleden
Video courtesy-Catherine Elliot I will show you pictures of my tongue cancer. Tongue cancer images of a young non-smoker, non-drinker are not easy to find online, so here you go. This is a photo album which acts as a timeline starting from my cancer diagnosis Halloween 2011 until my recovery one year later 2013. The most important thing is to diagnose EARLY and you will have a successful journey getting it removed and living life again! For more tips on self-screening, check out my friends site: ww.sixstepscreening.org/oral-cancer ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Publish all your dental videos and articles @ DentalMainframe.com and use our services to watermark and securely archive all your dental content for free.
